data.description: NEW PRICE REDUCTION!!!!! Bring your buyers to see this house in the highly sought after gated JP Ranch community.  The home is perfect for family, close to schools and shopping.  With a great view and 4 bdrms with 3 bathrooms with plenty of room for kids and guests. The roomy master bedroom has a large walk in closetincluding a barn door.  This home also has all the SMART HOME features. You will love the open concept with a large size great room that opens to the kitchen with laminate floors and granite counters  The low maintenance backyard has a view with no neighbors behind. Solar panels are included in the price. Has a great community pool and a gorgeous clubhouse .  Bring your decorating ideas and make this home yours!!
